Subject: RE: [VB] Rear Axle Nut

 A few things.

Parts place SUCKS A$$.Great place if you like paying more than list price
for things.

The 41mm nut is on the inside of the RGB not to be confused with the outer
axle nut which is either 46mm or 36mm.

You can get this from anyone stocking BugPack and I think Lisle Tools made
one too.

It is a tool of last resort for REMOVING the nuts not installing them.

Lastly PartsPlace inc./Jack Finn SUCKS A$$.

If I sound bitter your right.I worked there about 20 years ago and that guy
still pisses me off.


